                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Chấm công thành công!</h3>
                <p class="text-2xl text-green-400 mb-2" id="modalAction">Vào làm</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-300" id="modalTime"></p>
                <button onclick="closeSuccessModal()" class="mt-10 w-full py-4 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition transform hover:scale-105">
                    Đóng
